Thanks Ron you saved me alot of typing LOL

You are correct RJ, if you are still in the stage of how and why and looking for &quot;proof&quot; it is better to do experiments and sharing the way you describe. Go for it.

And Ron already knows me well. I am a little beyond caring how or why it works, or even asking spirits questions. I just record thier chatter, document for my own learning, and share with a few friends or persons its meant for privately. Once in a while I post samples for others who are curious about the different methods being used or new to the subject. 

I never expect anyone to hear anything as I do, its a nice surprise when someone does =)

Good luck!

Misty






